		<rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Relevant for legal analysis: true. The question was asked by a member of a given parliamentary group. Currently expressed in Procat as AF_GROUP, coded by FD Table 290. Relevant for legal analysis: true</rdfs:comment>
		<rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/cdmplus#ParliamentaryQuestion"/>
