		<rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Manifestation is part of manifestation</rdfs:label>
		<rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Relevant for legal analysis: true. The manifestation is part of another manifestation (e.g. the manifestation of an act is part of the manifestation of the OJ in print). Manifestation is part of another manifestation. In particular relevant for OJ manifestations. Relevant for legal analysis: true</rdfs:comment>
		<rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/cdmplus#Manifestation"/>
		<rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/cdmplus#Manifestation"/>
	</owl:ObjectProperty>
