		<rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">The work is part of another work (e.g. an article in a volume of proceedings or a split COM that is part of a multipart COM). In theory also LNKCES, LNKCDR, but those have 0% of usage.</rdfs:comment>
