		<rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">34 cases (2012-07-31). Example: 62009TN0293: "Partial annulment request 52009XC0521(05)". Relevant for legal analysis: true.</rdfs:comment>
		<rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/cdmplus#SourceOfLaw"/>
		<rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/cdmplus#CaseLaw"/>
