		<rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Relevant for legal analysis: true. partiallySuspends and suspends could be handled as subcases of a shared superProperty. SP (1) / subsequent related instrument. Relevant for legal analysis: true</rdfs:comment>
