		<rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">manifestation that reproduces another manifestation embodying the same expression of a work. Reciprocal relationship: reproduction of (manifestation) (after RDA J.4.2.)</rdfs:comment>
