		<rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">This dossier is under the responsibility of a given agent. mapped from /ns4:ecTransmissionRequest/transmission/workflow/extension/ns3:workflowAgent , subproperty of involves</rdfs:comment>
