		<rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">3868 cases (2010-07-27). Example: 62000J0368: "Failure by a Member State to fulfil its obligations - Quality of bathing water - Inadequate implementation of Directive 76/160/EEC."</rdfs:comment>
